Revision history for cbicall:

1.0.1  2026-0X-XX

    - Fix single-sample workflows to keep one sample name across FASTQs with different prefixes.
    - Fix mtDNA extraction from hg38 BAMs by selecting chrM instead of MT.
    - Migrate project documentation from MkDocs Material to Docusaurus.
    - Add a resource bundle catalog and record selected bundle provenance in run logs.
    - Improve external resource download, verification, extraction, and installation manifests.
    - Make the external resource downloader catalog-driven and add bundle identifier verification.
    - Add runtime profiles for site-specific environment files, including CNAG HPC.
    - Rename the workflow registry to workflows/registry/workflows.yaml.
    - Add explicit pipeline implementation versions in the workflow registry and run provenance.
    - Add doctor, validate-registry, and test helper commands.
    - Add compact run-report.json summaries for completed runs.

1.0.0  2026-03-23

    - First stable version released with pre-print.
